      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im having a really hard time sleeping lately. like i can barely stay asleep for more than a couple hours. i already take a melatonin pill every night but it doesnt seem to be doing much anymore. my doctor gave me some zolpidem (ambien) to help, but i was wondering if it's okay if i take the melatonin along with it? i figure if i take both it might actually work better since they both help with sleep. is that safe?",
