      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i just feel like they work differently so maybe they won't clash? like melatonin is just a hormone right and ambien is a sedative. i read online that people sometimes use them together to get a deeper sleep. are you sure it's actually dangerous or is it just something they tell everyone to avoid? i'm just desperate to actually get some rest.",
